casebody.data:
GREENWOOD NURSERY, INC., a Texas corporation, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. HOME DEPOT U.S.A., INC., a Georgia corporation, Defendant-Appellee. No. 08-15582

Non-Argument Calendar.

United States Court of Appeals, Eleventh Circuit. Feb. 17, 2009. John W. Davis, Jr., Davis & Melton, P.C., Dalton, GA, Michael D. Martin, Martin Law Office, Lakeland, FL, for Plaintiff-Appellant. Lisa R. Strauss, Ronan P. Doherty, Bon-durant, Mixson & Elmore, LLP, Atlanta, GA, for Defendant-Appellee. ■ Before TJOFLAT, CARNES and WILSON, Circuit Judges. PER CURIAM:

The judgment of the district court is affirmed. Appellant’s claims are barred for the reasons the district court spelled out in its order of September 4, 2008, 2008 WL 4181186.

AFFIRMED.
